{
  "stem": "27335.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had this-- this lordly-- lordly castles and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were several of them then-- then for the duration.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they converted them into-- into training schools, you see?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had most our-- most of intelligent training, you see?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the funniest thing that-- that we had on the-- on the real intelligence work, you see, how-- how-- how spies work, we had to know some-- something of it, because we had to make-- make contacts.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And our instructor was Kim Philby.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know it at the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all the- all the time that I found out years-- many years later, you know, when he was exposed as a-- as a so-called Soviet spy.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And see-- see his picture in-- in and look and look and turn away and looked again.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, he's dumb, and sure enough there a doubt to be that-- that he was-- he was-- well, he was in full confidence at the-- at the time.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And did you trust him as a-- as a real master spy, you see?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "To give-- Did he-- did he give you his name?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Did you know his name?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My dear, as soon as-- as soon as-- back here, it was all right.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But as soon as we landed in-- landed in England, well we had to-- had to strip our-- our real names.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- and I had about six names by the time I got through this whole-- whole-- whole business.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, he-- he told us-- but not-- not in a class, but in the-- how much he talked to others, but for the two of us who he himself picked, well, these are the two-- two-- two-- the two-- two-- top ones.",
      "word_count": 43
    }
  ],
